OL,3,C'Science doesn't back it': Doctors
OL,4,Ccall for ban on smacking children in
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FLeading doctors have called for the
OL,8,F"Victorian" punishment of smacking
OL,9,Fchildren to be banned in England as it
OL,10,Fputs them at risk of "really
OL,11,Fsignificant physical harm".
OL,13,FWales made any type of corporal
OL,14,Fpunishment, including smacking,
OL,15,Fhitting, slapping and shaking, illegal
OL,16,Fin March 2022, while Scotland
OL,17,Fintroduced a similar ban in November
OL,18,F2020.
