OL,3,C'Science doesn't back it': Doctors
OL,4,Ccall for ban on smacking children in
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FThe Royal College of Paediatrics and
OL,8,FChild Health (RCPCH) has called for
OL,9,Fthe ban to be introduced in England,
OL,10,Fwith one senior doctor making an
OL,11,Femotional appeal to politicians.
OL,13,FMedics urged those opposing a smacking
OL,14,Fban to consider the scientific
OL,15,Fevidence, which shows that smacking
OL,16,Fcauses both physical and emotional
OL,17,Fharm and "doesn't benefit them in any
OL,18,Fway whatsoever".
