OL,3,C'Science doesn't back it': Doctors
OL,4,Ccall for ban on smacking children in
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,F"Now is the time for this Victorian-
OL,8,Fera punishment to go and the
OL,9,FChildren's Wellbeing and Schools Bill
OL,10,Famendment will do that if passed."
OL,12,FHe said 67 countries have already
OL,13,Fintroduced smacking bans, with another
OL,14,F20 planning to do so.
OL,16,F"The best scientific evidence I've got
OL,17,Fis that physical punishment of
OL,18,Fchildren undoubtedly harms children's
OL,19,Fhealth on a population basis," Prof
OL,20,FRowland said.
