OL,7,F"It harms their physical health,
OL,8,Fplaces them at increased risk of
OL,9,Fserious physical assault, it harms
OL,10,Ftheir mental health and it harms their
OL,11,Femotional health and their wellbeing `
OL,12,Fall of that is shown in robust
OL,13,Fscientific evidence.
OL,15,F"There have been no robust scientific
OL,16,Fstudies that have shown that physical
OL,17,Fpunishment of children has any
