OL,7,FAsked about the case, Professor
OL,8,FRowland said: "What happened to Sara
OL,9,Fwas absolutely horrendous, and I can
OL,10,Fsay that as a paediatrician, but also
OL,11,Fas a member of the public, that no
OL,12,Fchild should suffer as Sara suffered.
OL,14,F"Unrelated to Sara's case, we know
OL,15,Fthat the international evidence is
OL,16,Fthat children who are physically
OL,17,Fpunished are at risk of serious
OL,18,Fphysical assault ` that's been shown
OL,19,Facademically."
