OL,4,Ccall for ban on smacking children in
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FJoanna Barrett, associate head of
OL,8,Fpolicy at the NSPCC, said: "We stand
OL,9,Fin support of the Royal College's
OL,10,Fcalls for children to be given the
OL,11,Fsame protection against physical
OL,12,Fpunishment as adults, and it's clear
OL,13,Fthe obvious next step is to amend the
OL,14,FChildren's Wellbeing and Schools Bill
OL,15,Fto remove the 'reasonable punishment'
OL,16,Fdefence.
