OL,3,C'Science doesn't back it': Doctors
OL,4,Ccall for ban on smacking children in
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,F"Physical punishment can have a
OL,8,Fdetrimental impact on a child's
OL,9,Fwellbeing. It has been associated with
OL,10,Fdepression, anxiety, increased
OL,11,Faggression and anti-social behaviour.
OL,13,F"Legal change must happen urgently,
OL,14,Fbecause right now we know physical
OL,15,Fpunishment remains a part of childhood
OL,16,Ffor too many young people in England."
